徘徊，立法者......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/20 /24135163/tiktok-ban-divest-bytedance-house-foreign-aid-package&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/20/24135163/tiktok-ban-divest-bytedance-house-foreign-aid-package" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/20/24135163/tiktok-ban-divest-bytedance-house-foreign-aid-package</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-20T13:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-20T13:00:00-04:00</updated><title>扎克·施奈德的《反叛月亮》电影对影迷构成威胁</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个穿着背心、战斗腰带和裤子的女人，拿着两把枪站在某种控制室里。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EVdW60pC_eX1aYOy79onij8SDio=/0x0:7200x4800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73292987/RBM_20221019_43454_R_CC.0。 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Netflix&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Netflix 的《反叛月亮》电影都感觉像是扎克·施奈德试图通过以一些最缺乏灵感的方式轻轻地重复它们来庆祝科幻经典。&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24134948/netflix-zack-snyder-rebel-moon-2-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24134948/netflix-zack-snyder-rebel-moon-2-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24134948/netflix-zack-snyder-rebel-moon-2-review</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-20T12:42:08-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-20T12:42:08-04:00</updated><title> 《深夜与魔鬼》中冷静的恐怖</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;演员 Ingrid Torelli、David Dastmalchian 和 Laura Gordon 在《与魔鬼的光夜》中的剧照。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Xi92xvQG5ZE6LUnRz7x25IvtmjM=/0x24:2700x1824/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73292948/LNWTD___3.0.jpeg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;由 IFC Films 和 Shudder 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;MSVwo7&quot;>;恐怖电影的生与死取决于其自负。有时，让电影变得恐怖的最好方法就是将其